The soundtrack had six songs and an instrumental theme (which was only included in the cassettes), composed by [[A. R. Rahman]] with lyrics by [[Vairamuthu]]. The songs were later reused in the [[Hindi language|Hindi]] movie ''[[Vishwavidhaata]]''. The soundtrack received very positive responses and is regarded as a classic work by A.R. Rahman. The soundtrack was also released in [[Telugu language|Telugu]] as ''Padmavyuham'', with lyrics were by [[Rajashri|Rajashree]].

